Package gr.aueb.cf.reviewapp.service.dto.registration

package gr.aueb.cf.reviewapp.service.dto.registration
The service.dto.registration package contains class definitions for DTOs returned to the frontend during the user registration process.
  • Classes
    Class
    Description
    RegBaseDTO
    The RegBaseDTO abstract class enables subtype polymorphism for DTO implementations.
    UserRegBadDataDTO
    The UserRegBadDataDTO class is returned by the UserRestController to the frontend if the received UserInsertDTO contains invalid data.
    UserRegFailureDTO
    The UserRegFailureDTO class is returned by the UserRestController to the frontend if the received UserInsertDTO contains a username that is already persisted.
    UserRegSuccessDTO
    The UserRegSuccessDTO class is returned by the UserRestController to the frontend if the received UserInsertDTO is valid and the user is successfully persisted.
